        %h3.ui.header Our Mission
        %p
          We are a team of people under the auspices of The Journey Church who
          are sponsoring a refugee family or families to settle in
          Moncton or surrounding area.
        %p
          Thank you to everyone who has helped with this project.
          The sponsored family has been in Moncton since early August and are
          in the process of adjusting to life in Canada.
          The children have settled into school and the family is improving their knowledge of both English and French.
        %p
          We will be hosting a welcome party in the next few weeks, and everyone who has helped in any way is
          invited to come, meet the family, and hear some of their story of their journey from Syria to Canada.
          As soon as we have a date and location set, we'll be posting it on this website and on Facebook.
