        %h3 How Can I Help?
        %p
          We are looking for lightly used winter clothing:
          %ul
            %li
              %p
                Girls size 6-7, boots size 13-14.
                She has a snowsuit, but needs a winter coat, and kids can't have too many mittens,
                toques, hats, scarves, socks and an extra pair of boots.
            %li
              %p
                Boys size 11-12, boots size 6 - he also has a snowsuit, but again, a winter coat is needed,
                as well as extra mittens, hats, etc.
            %li
              %p
                Ladies size small (winter coat, boots, and hats, gloves, scarves, etc).
        %p
          Also looking for volunteers who would be available to drive to afternoon appointments occasionally.
          If you can help out, please email Caitlin Dawe at
          %a(href="mailto:caitlin.dawe@gmail.com") caitlin.dawe@gmail.com
        %p
          From a financial perspective, while we have raised all the funds necessary to support the family for
          their first 12 months, the travel costs to get to Canada were quite a bit higher than expected,
          due to changes to government policy after March 2016, and also due to some urgency in booking
          travel out of Lebanon. Because of this, we are still accepting donations to help offset that extra expense.

